title: Castle Wolfenstein
description:
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

1. Mount or burn "Return To Castle Wolfenstein - Updates included" with DAEMON TOOLS or other program for mounting.
2. Run keygen in Crack & Keygen folder - write the key down.
3. Run AUTORUN from image/disk and install. Use the key you just wrote down.
4. Patch up to v.1.4 using patches in WolfUD folder.
5. Copy and paste "WolfSP" and "WolfMP" from Crack & KeygenFixes folder into the now-installed Wolfenstein folder.
6. Enjoy!


Warning:1.Don't shut down the computer on INSTALLATION. 
        2.Befor start INSTALLING, disable your antvirus!
